long_description: The PhiNesse eyelashes are natural and handmade. Each eyelash is made to look as natural as possible. The eyelashes are soft, flexible, easy to apply and comfortable to wear.Specially designed to enhance your moment. The lashes then appear longer, thicker, darker and fuller, can also be used to make your look more glamorous.
